* **`curl http://127.0.0.1:2379/v2/keys/foo -XPUT -d value=one`**
* **`curl http://127.0.0.1:2379/v2/keys/foo?prevIndex=96 -XDELETE`**
* **`curl http://127.0.0.1:2379/v2/keys/foo`**
